subject: [ANN] Version 0.3a of Java Gui Builder released !
msgSnippet: This new version boasts the following features: - Support for event handling; - Major refactorings for tag handlers; - More complete examples; - Completely
messageBody:
This new version boasts the following features:
- Support for event handling;
- Major refactorings for tag handlers;
- More complete examples;
- Completely redesigned web-site.

You may download this new version at
http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=50316&release_id=88479

I encourage you to subscribe to the jgb-announce list if you want to keep
informed of the latest revision of the Java Gui Builder.

Thank you,
Francois Beausoleil
Java Gui Builder - http://jgb.sourceforge.net/
